title: Raiders Saints Recap, Pep Talks and TNF Preview
itunes:title: Raiders Saints Recap, Pep Talks and TNF Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, and Marc Sessler are joined by Colleen Wolfe to recap the Raiders first game in the Death Star and how they overcame the Saints (4:35). The heroes give someone a much needed Pep Talk going into Week 3 (22:07) before previewing the big Florida bowl matchup on Thursday night (45:00).
